{"tid":2499603,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"畢業多年嘅老鬼有咩同大學生講？","createTime":"2021-04-22T04:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T04:46:44.000Z","uid":71237,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3e21b164578baff6d221cbaf88ba7f6d03b10184","tid":2499603,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:34:07.000Z","msg":"琴日見到有個post叫「畢業多年嘅老鬼有咩同中學生講？」(<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2498602/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2498602/page/1</a>)，大家又有咩想同大學生講？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我先：<br />\n唔好太抗拒喺私人公司返工。見過有啲大學生以為喺私人公司返工一定要爾虞我詐、唯利是圖。以為喺啲唔賺錢嘅機構工作(例如做老師)啲同事先會係好人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無錯，私人公司係以賺錢為目標，但唔代表喺私人公司返工嘅人都係勢利、埋沒良心。<br />\n<br />\n而且就算你工作嘅機構唔係以賺錢為目標，例如學校、政府、公營機構、NGO，都唔代表啲人就係好人。有時學校入面勾心鬥角嘅問題比私人公司更加嚴重。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71dad68061ca8b303e4adf70aedfe24b93d109cb","tid":2499603,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:35:32.000Z","msg":"如果你以為做銀行 = 衰人，做老師 / 醫護 = 好人<br />\n就你真係太天真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bff74210f852338a1e3c36ac21b04879fccf64","tid":2499603,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:40:05.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"dcdc83804874309315241d455159612bb38c881d","tid":2499603,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:44:30.000Z","msg":"英文好好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得揀專科"},{"pid":"427b1097a6325b094a8c50136112c562c6287a3d","tid":2499603,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:46:00.000Z","msg":"溫書啦柒頭"},{"pid":"85dc52cc79e2da6bbad262c3c9ad62dea82be094","tid":2499603,"uid":149673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:46:44.000Z","msg":"唔好以為自己有degree就好巴閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}